Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音變清脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？放任一色真那樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做的那些事，稍微有些過火…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是她的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海倫娜，該是時候去做準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是你的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東大尉，我想請你離開TERRA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由我不說你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為你是個更聰明一些的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你好啊，遙小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這裡的事情就交給八雲你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為科學調查部的報告怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，請您去指揮中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合統轄部的來電
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，Down Fall作戰的實施時間提前1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個命令嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在到消滅作戰艦隊的旗艦去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那裡進行指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去莉麗亞·立特巴克號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親眼目睹我們的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過於努力對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再介意那件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，如果你覺得那樣比較好的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…姐姐她去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道？姐姐被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她惹惱了白蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，反正今天我休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙小姐的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蛇囉嗦了好幾次，要我趕快把這些處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的氣量真小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…這個給你，這是遙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面的照片好像很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就幫她收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~怎麼會丟在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們是姐妹，這種事也不能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀啊！姐姐好年輕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾啊…太狡猾了，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你們認識的時間)比我的人生還長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能贏你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六道家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父他不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這盒子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡貓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鳥的地方，養貓的確不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美智留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「Tyltyl和Mytyl」的Mytyl嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:08.15,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}Tyltyl和Mytyl：比利時法語作家莫裡斯·梅特林克(Maurice Maeterlinck)\N的著名童話劇《青鳥(L'oiseau Bleu)》中的主角\N伐木工人的兒子(TylTyl)和女兒(Mytyl)\NMytyl和美智留的日語發音都是「」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我女兒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東大尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有她的話，你早就被送進收容所了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，如果追究起你洩漏最高機密的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被處以極刑也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就想問您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生，您家的櫻樹真的是開藍色的花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的？這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹博士對大家說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊，這種荒誕的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來功刀先生也有笑的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有機會我們一起去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前就是如此，像現在這樣相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡美人和奈利亞神殿的黑色卵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我交給巴貝姆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有各式各樣的不同的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當她到了17歲時，意識到了那一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一個在命運中的王子到來之前就已經醒來的睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時…我以為只能這麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要責怪自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他之間的往來，我盡可能地寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓你回想起討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果，我就是這種女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和父親的事情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在財團做TDD的基礎研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為事故去世了，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不是什麼事故…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺了他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於是我殺了他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時，巴貝姆財團的人對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做是為了父親他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會保障他們的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果麵包掉在了地上，塗黃油一面肯定是朝下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是重複著這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個人也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹君對小夜子你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹君！樹君！樹君！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是叫他樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我總是叫他樹先生、樹老師、如月博士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你…其實我很討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白小夜子你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太差勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁的人是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就快超過17歲而失去奏者的資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留給我們的時間已經不多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人做為人類的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使時間很短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想把他當作自家人一起過普通的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對我來說，就像我的孫子一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我沒能對女兒盡到義務所作的一點補償吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算在那裡站到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一段時間想避開你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等畫完成了，你能第一個來看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士的JB-3，啟動準備完畢
